cast.overview: A young street-smart, Nathan Drake and his wisecracking partner Victor “Sully” Sullivan embark on a dangerous pursuit of “the greatest treasure never found” while also tracking clues that may lead to Nathan’s long-lost brother.
cast.title: Uncharted

details.biography: Alana Evie Boden (born January 14, 1997) is a British actress. She began her career as a child model before moving to television commercials and short films. She is known for appearing in a variety of television shows and films, such as Uncharted, Flowers in the Attic: The Origin, The Invitation, and Geek Girl.
details.name: Alana Boden
